===Etymology===
From Greek φαντασμα phantasma (ghost) + αγορευειν agoreuein (to speak publicly)

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ˌfæntæzməˈgɒriə/}} (''[[RP]]'')
*{{IPA|/ˌfæntæzməˈgɔːriə/}} (''US'')
